The component confirms hypothesis 1: each click changes that button’s accessible name (`Mark Uploaded` → `Uploaded`), so Playwright’s pre-collected `nth()` locators re-index against a shrinking match set. I’m applying a two-line behavioral fix to the test helper: repeatedly click the current first matching action until none remain. No production code or styling changes are needed.
